{"word":"G1928 - ἐπιδιατάσσομαι - epidiatássomai - ep-ee-dee-ah-tas'-som-ahee - Add to","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιδιατάσσομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epidiatássomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-dee-ah-tas'-som-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Add to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கூட்டு"},{"paragraph":"to ordain besides"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G1299 - διατάσσω - diatássō - dee-at-as'-so/1299\">G1299</a>; to <i>appoint besides</i>, that is, <i>supplement</i> (as a codicil): - add to.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}